moxie.hamcrest

Class IsArrayWithSize<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hamcrest.BaseMatcher<T>
      • org.hamcrest.TypeSafeMatcher<T>
        • moxie.hamcrest.IsArrayWithSize<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the array to be matched (NOT the element type of the array)
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.hamcrest.Matcher<T>, org.hamcrest.SelfDescribing

    public class IsArrayWithSize<T>
extends org.hamcrest.TypeSafeMatcher<T>
    Matches any array (including primitive arrays) whose size satisfies a nested Matcher.

    Intended as a substitute for Hamcrest's IsArrayWithSize - unlike the original, this class can work with primitive arrays as well as arrays of objects.
